_json.gridTitle: Capsicum Masala Curry Recipe - With Roasted Sesame Seeds and Peanut Based Spicy Masala
_json.description: Capsicum Masala Curry 2 medium Green Capsicum (green bell peppers/shimla mirch) 2 teaspoons Coriander Seeds 1 tablespoon grated Dry Coconut 1 Dry Red Chilli 1 teaspoon Sesame Seeds 1/4 cup Roasted Peanuts 1/2 teaspoon Cumin Seeds (jeera) 1 medium Onion, finely chopped 2 cloves Garlic, crushed 1/2 teaspoon Red Chilli Powder (lal mirch) 1/4 teaspoon Turmeric Powder (haldi) 1/2 teaspoon Lemon Juice 1 teaspoon Sugar 2 tablespoons Cooking Oil Salt 3/4 cup Water
